name: The Second G O D - Habibi
description: As a huge fan of The Habibi Workshop, myself and  @mgmm  have teamed up to create the G O D Habibi, a rare, fan made, limited edition collectable.  @mgmm  created the uniqe music accompanying the piece and is the owner of 'The Rave' Habibi which was made by  @MarkTheHabibi  &  @disclosure  to represent the creative culture both visual and acoustic.
